30
0:01:41.760 --> 0:01:47.120
So it's what you learn from your family, from your friends, from your school, your city,

31
0:01:47.120 --> 0:01:50.560
your state, your country, that all have a culture that influences you and helps you

32
0:01:50.560 --> 0:01:55.320
