0:13:48.920 --> 0:13:56.920
As I said Melville Herskovitz was a student of Franz Boas and my parents' instructor.

185
0:13:56.920 --> 0:14:03.600
So let's look at a couple of examples of cultural relativism in cross-cultural teams.

186
0:14:03.600 --> 0:14:11.600
I worked on a project where we were transitioning the development from one culture to another.

187
0:14:11.600 --> 0:14:16.360
