189
0:14:21.360 --> 0:14:24.560
This was a career limiting move.

190
0:14:24.560 --> 0:14:27.880
Don't fail, don't show failure.

191
0:14:27.880 --> 0:14:31.240
It was also not acceptable to disagree with somebody who is perceived to be of a higher

192
0:14:31.240 --> 0:14:34.640
rank or status.

193
0:14:34.640 --> 0:14:38.440
And we're trying to do open source development where everybody does everything in the public

194
0:14:38.440 --> 0:14:41.640
so that you can see what's happening.

195
0:14:41.640 --> 0:14:46.200
So this was a problem for us as we're trying to move this across.

196
0:14:46.200 --> 0:14:52.280
And so we came up with a couple of techniques that we used in this project to get around

197
0:14:52.280 --> 0:14:53.280
this problem.

198
0:14:53.280 --> 0:14:56.600
One was actually understanding what the problem was.

199
0:14:56.600 --> 0:14:59.200
