200
0:14:59.200 --> 0:15:01.240
I don't want to do this, I won't do that.

201
0:15:01.240 --> 0:15:02.240
Why?

202
0:15:02.240 --> 0:15:03.240
Because we just don't do that.

203
0:15:03.240 --> 0:15:05.920
And then you have to work a little bit.

204
0:15:05.920 --> 0:15:13.160
You find out what the problems are at the base and figure out how you can work a solution.

205
0:15:13.160 --> 0:15:17.680
So what we did was we made it safe to fail and we exhibited failures on the original

206
0:15:17.680 --> 0:15:18.680
team.

