0:15:44.760 --> 0:15:45.760
can you help me out?

217
0:15:45.760 --> 0:15:46.760
They're going to come look.

218
0:15:46.760 --> 0:15:49.040
But otherwise they're going to ignore that.

219
0:15:49.040 --> 0:15:50.040
Don't worry about it.

220
0:15:50.040 --> 0:15:51.040
It's safe.

221
0:15:51.040 --> 0:15:58.240
We were we pointed out that developers were not allowed to change the main branch of code.

